SELECT MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment, SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS sum_s_s_acctbal, MAX(s.s_suppkey) AS max_s_s_suppkey, l.l_discount AS l_l_discount, l.l_shipmode AS l_l_shipmode, s.s_nationkey AS SELECT COUNT(l.l_suppkey) AS count_l_l_suppkey, COUNT(l.l_comment) AS count_l_l_comment, MAX(l.l_shipinstruct) AS max_l_l_shipinstruct, p.p_retailprice AS p_p_retailprice, AVG(l.l_quantity) AS
